想啊，人哋只係唔再補習姐，就係要整死佢先安樂😭😭呢個世界真係咩人都有"},{"pid":"39352b48cc28f464eed21832493ba16f1e8bb734","tid":152912,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8059b169e83a14dc4bcca10a267710aaf7869e3d","tid":152912,"uid":88126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 垃圾教畜害人不淺 啲老師真係好撚戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要係之前學校啲代課老師⋯"},{"pid":"8816e6e1859b921207dc0f5a87213b6dabb00542","tid":152912,"uid":3419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"抵撚死喇 繼續揾要女唔要男喇 繼續揾d臭閪幫你地啲死𡃁仔補喇 男又要miss 女要miss"},{"pid":"936a446372178d1c25a6fd5e078fdae98881f783","tid":152912,"uid":88126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明佢真係有咁既程度咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?對住啲老師作篇文</blockquote><br />\n所以淨係寫咗篇匿名信，不負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全沒有證據下誣告他人"},{"pid":"5d95107db1b55203c2c08eabc00fef54a793f00a","tid":152912,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人是非真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n妒忌就無視正邪，都唔知佢哋個腦點運作<br />\n<br />\n癡撚線"},{"pid":"b146c5f91ee7c0e146025285bf56b39b661f1106","tid":152912,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>女人是非真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n妒忌就無視正邪，都唔知佢哋個腦點運作<br />\n<br />\n癡撚線</blockquote><br />\n女人係咁撚樣<br />\n留明睇更加多受害學生<br />\n還男人一個公道"},{"pid":"cb06fc63c9bdf7b806caaf9b3997078896ee7811","tid":152912,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:53:14.000Z","msg":"同佢傾下計 開解下 輔導下佢 引佢講自己野 上堂情況等等<br />\n<br />\n係學校同學又會信佢出貓咁戇鳩既<br />\n把口生係人度冇得控制<br />\n唯有叫佢唔好太介意，相信自己做好自己就得<br />\n<br />\n時間一過就好好多<br />\n<br />\n傾計鳩up已經好好喇其實"},{"pid":"1bf0bd64323d6180d234d199494b881060ee011f","tid":152912,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:57:14.000Z","msg":"仲有佢家長呢，搵機會同佢家長傾下<br />\n<br />\n八下佢屋企個一面係點<br />\n<br />\n了解多啲佢，多啲野講又清楚佢既想法都好<br />\n<br />\n比啲assurance 比佢，等佢知道萬大事除左屋企人朋友，補習哥哥/姐姐都係一個可靠既渠道（我有時睇得出啲學生有困難，受壓力，我會話「等哥哥同你一齊面對」，類似既說話）"},{"pid":"14c2b86c7ba7f672423a078db196b317dec41c8c","tid":152912,"uid":2869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"同囤地波單野有啲似<br />\n可唔可以告個老師誹謗？"},{"pid":"ea9bd377978a02b1ee9b032f8e576b509a155b8b","tid":152912,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:03:25.000Z","msg":"又係學校野<br />\n<br />\n而家d學校愈黎愈麻煩，細路仔都要搞。<br />\n<br />\n樓主你搵定d詳細資料證明你講既野先，唔好放出黎住，等多d人先。<br />\n<br />\n推上熱門"},{"pid":"dda0c054e388c2ebeb420f7e195a5c7517b00e54","tid":152912,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"個個咩補習咁巴閉，自己無料到就話人。<br />\n<br />\n學校又係唔知咩事，樓主你點知學校老師傳去其他人度？有無details？呢d好重要。<br />\n<br />\n其他野都無咁嬲，一講到學校野，仲要咁細個都比人玩就好忟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7733c333cd5d4cc11bcde1cc40f03c4899afaf84","tid":152912,"uid":34782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"轉校"},{"pid":"5e6cbaa43be5aaf22032d8ac37c4d6dac4ba7b80","tid":152912,"uid":29335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"小學英文可以點出貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由得佢哋講囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98296d536ac9fd33ab78b8a95e13f9d75c03483b","tid":152912,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:29:03.000Z","msg":"咁既仆街都學人做教畜 遺禍人間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 其實做補習教畜姐 個家長炒佢又唔係個學生炒<br />\n為冇左果$1xx/ hour 既唔忿氣而搞尻個細路<br />\n小心將來生仔冇屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d30c71b336ea6e88b49d20cb6f8497b17693ab","tid":152912,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:35:42.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e380612a454e8f992dcf519ad5f0551a458efd","tid":152912,"uid":63995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"呢個真係要公審<br />\n小朋友會好大陰影"},{"pid":"6080c61ec42871d7ce54b74231c833f0c5639b35","tid":152912,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"你又唔俾名 電話黎 點幫你報仇呀"},{"pid":"14da310582ef0429174e2aee5f96050e2aa18991","tid":152912,"uid":16560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"3e1e50e84ac2891de94c71221982440ed661fd1b","tid":152912,"uid":88126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有佢家長呢，搵機會同佢家長傾下<br />\n<br />\n八下佢屋企個一面係點<br />\n<br />\n了解多啲佢，多啲野講又清楚佢既想法都好<br />\n<br />\n比啲assurance 比佢，等佢知道萬大事除左屋企人朋友，補習哥哥/姐姐都係一個可靠既渠道（我有時睇得出啲學生有困難，受壓力，我會話「等哥哥同你一齊面對」，類似既說話）</blockquote><br />\nThanks！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49adecf3897ef9b42c148382d066809b15c3d215","tid":152912,"uid":88126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係學校野<br />\n<br />\n而家d學校愈黎愈麻煩，細路仔都要搞。<br />\n<br />\n樓主你搵定d詳細資料證明你講既野先，唔好放出黎住，等多d人先。<br />\n<br />\n推上熱門</blockquote><br />\n但係佢係匿名信，我哋知道謠言散播姐，都算係100%肯定，但係始終信箱亦冇名，要追究責任亦不容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf39f141801125b2a4ec28c8d6178f7a9e02aaa0","tid":152912,"uid":6558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"幫推 真係好撚仆街"},{"pid":"08f63760b1cc0c2fb0a73353db3f86fdbc21ca16","tid":152912,"uid":6558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60cb24dfd2835cd0a44dc4e0d0857fab4b38071","tid":152912,"uid":6558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b271a4ab5aaec30628def4d40c90f8a80be290c4","tid":152912,"uid":12221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"其實去到呢個地步已經做唔到啲咩 學校冇介入調查 啲老師仲走去問個小朋友補習搵咩人 唔知頭唔知路懷疑佢 講真好冇質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學生出貓呢啲 啲老師睇實佢幾次都睇得出係真定假啦<br />\n唯有靠屋企人同好似你呢啲比較親近既話佢知 呢啲流言好快過 最緊要做好自己 捱到畢業 或者過一個暑假就會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於你話想爆個補習老師大鑊 寄個封係匿名信 冇證據既話 就算你提出合理懷疑都難令人信服<br />\n多口問句 佢而家係學校同班係咪已經冇人同佢玩？<br />\n你都要加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  小朋友靠你同佢屋企人支持"},{"pid":"3eac93143d1c01d103ef437eeb3ab0151cd85a52","tid":152912,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:27:43.000Z","msg":"無啦啦係到屌女人，成班傻鳩"},{"pid":"70533f98cc12fd1c7dacc784b4502a66b2a19e1f","tid":152912,"uid":35069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"成件事都係以極端路向走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家庭又係，個補習老師又係。好多野都係需要平衡，唔係咩做到最好就係，表面上係好好，但係一有d咩突發嘢係非常容易令到呢d人諗埋一邊做傻事，所以好多天才都係好早死，因為佢地平衡唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲早又係跳樓果堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04b6feeb93a30c36cb4e2b5aa15d4bcbcb507fe","tid":152912,"uid":39262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"唔怪得知咁多細路自殺，都係類似呢啲仆街幫手，估唔到宜家學校複雜到咁既地步，唉......"},{"pid":"01cc2e1b130c843668166aaf19832ae00751ea79","tid":152912,"uid":81617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:37:37.000Z","msg":"報警，最簡單"},{"pid":"463088a79cdc97a7924e78cacb40991f19beeaa7","tid":152912,"uid":81617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"樓主不如開條臭閪名＋資料"},{"pid":"f0cff937dd8ac78c2d1735bcb9bdca12a58b94c9","tid":152912,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:48:09.000Z","msg":"條臭閪死教畜都好意思做人老師幫人補習<br />\n垃圾家長唔抵得人地d仔女叻過自己果個<br />\n樓主點都唔可以唔理個學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  10歲就要承受咁多野真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f1dbc4363b5bcb796b8601e41329d591cd9b08","tid":152912,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"即場考一次，如果成績好，叫有份講是非嘅人當場呃喺度認錯"},{"pid":"af9312971035f7b03c85ef68d1dbfb9acd58c7ee","tid":152912,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:15:55.000Z","msg":"既然佢咁醒<br />\n都唔怕話埋比佢知呢個世界係咁<br />\n有料自然有D人想做低你"},{"pid":"791f25e84f80ce9eb632f04e672ac02bca777c5a","tid":152912,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我哋一齊幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95be4332051c90d668eef21e1f6d758dcea6e51d","tid":152912,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:50:35.000Z","msg":"係到開一開個臭閪名 <br />\n就解決啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843bdbb933a54155d334affe3f83741d43082fe1","tid":152912,"uid":33563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"學校最怕家長<br />\n叫佢屋企人突擊踩上去嘈+疲勞轟炸<br />\n又屌又哭喪講小朋友被欺凌<br />\n見完班主任再見校長，再叫校長比小朋友見學校社工<br />\n做齊三部曲就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔驚第日老師比面色小朋友，實怕家長又同校長嘈<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n小學遇過精神病老師+比人欺凌過"},{"pid":"eaeda91bc2e711d03a91d907675b625508c56e91","tid":152912,"uid":8748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:02:17.000Z","msg":"放嗰條臭雞上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌佢老母 攪細佬哥咁撚冇人性"},{"pid":"765b5aff2ddd03e30f37441e7f1f9c511c869446","tid":152912,"uid":64523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T12:10:41.000Z","msg":"正臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}